text: Welcome to TK Trails a private, legacy-caliber equine estate offering 5.5 acres of luxury, seclusion, and unmatched access to the natural beauty of North Texas. Surrounded on three sides by federally owned, Army Corps of Engineersmanaged land along the shoreline of Lake Grapevine, this setting is rare, protected, and irreplaceable. With gated access into thousands of acres of preserved parks, wildlife habitat, and miles of riding and hiking trails, TK Trails blends complete privacy with boundless outdoor freedom. At the heart of the property stands a fully custom, state-of-the-art barn and covered arena purpose-built for performance, yet crafted with the detail of a fine estate home. Chandeliers, stamped concrete alleys, climate-controlled tack and medical rooms, and thoughtfully designed stall systems reflect unmatched attention to quality and functionality. A beautifully appointed 1-bedroom, 1-bath apartment provides quiet, private accommodations for a trainer, caretaker, or guest, with sweeping views of both the barn interior and arena. Beyond its equestrian excellence, TK Trails offers gated entry, concrete drives, irrigated paddocks, pipe fencing, two wells, and a serene pond creating a property that is both functional and luxurious. What truly sets TK Trails apart is its location. Few properties in North Texas enjoy this level of adjacency to Corps land and fewer still offer private keypad access to miles of protected shoreline trails along Lake Grapevine. All just 13 miles from DFW International Airport, 5.5 miles from Southlake Town Square, and 5 miles from the exclusive Vaquero Club. TK Trails is more than an equestrian estate it is a once-in-a-generation offering, a sanctuary of space, security, and purpose-built luxury destined to be treasured for years to come.

text: Luxury living at its finest in this custom estate nestled on a heavily treed 1-acre lot in the prestigious Southlake Woods community. Designed for both everyday comfort and grand-scale entertaining, this home features a gourmet kitchen with high-end stainless steel appliances, an oversized island, and open-concept living spaces with panoramic views of the backyard oasis. The owner's retreat offers a serene escape with a fireplace, private balcony, sitting area, and spa-inspired bath with soaking tub, walk-in shower, and dual vanities. Unique features include a 1, 000-bottle wine room, cigar humidor, state-of-the-art media room, game room, and a flexible space ideal for a gym or creative studio. Step outside to a Claffey-designed pool and spa with slide and firepit, outdoor living area with full kitchen, a Nicklaus Design putting green with chipping boxes, and a Rhino sport court. Interior finishes include limestone and hardwood floors, a marble fireplace imported from Siberia, and stainless steel accents from Scotland. Conveniently located near top-rated Carroll ISD schools, dining, shopping, and DFW Airport, this one-of-a-kind home offers the best of luxury and lifestyle in Southlake.

text: Discover timeless luxury & thoughtful design at 1006 Quail Run Road, a fully reimagined 9, 763 sqft estate situated on a beautifully treed 2.56 acre lot in the heart of Southlake's Quail Creek Estates. Originally built in 1987 & extensively renovated from 20212025 by the current owners in partnership with Bohanon Design Team, this 7-bed, 10-bath residence blends sophisticated & clean-lined architecture with top-tier infrastructure & finishes. From the moment you enter, youre greeted by natural light & sweeping views, thanks to 124 Anderson E-Series windows throughout. The home showcases a commissioned walnut-and-steel staircase & oversized kitchen island by Stahl Custom Lumber. The residence features 3.5 distinct kitchen & prep areas including a full main kitchen, an entertainment suite-MIL setup, outdoor kitchen & upstairs parlor. Interior highlights include 10ft ceilings, a Level 5 sheetrock finish, quartz window ledges, in-wall vacuum system with Hide-A-Hose tech, connections for 2 washer-dryer sets, hand-scraped white oak floors upstairs & finished concrete on the ground levelno carpet throughout. Cat-V wiring, Google Fire-Emissions detection & Savant media systems elevate everyday living, while sound-dampening insulation ensures privacy across all living & entertainment zones. Every detail was upgraded95% of wiring, all plumbing including a fire suppression system, four new HVAC units, foam encapsulation from roof to base & central steel beams designed to exceed 5x load requirements. The outdoor oasis is just as impressive. The backyard features a 45, 000-gallon, 10ft deep pool & spa with recently upgraded saltwater equipment, a custom Ipe diving dock, lush landscaping with mature oaks & Japanese maples & a turf athletic field with walking track & bleachers installed by the same professionals behind the Frisco Star. With no expense spared & no detail overlooked, this is truly a rare opportunity to own a contemporary, one-of-a-kind estate in Southlake, Texas.

text: A True Southlake Masterpiece in Prestigious Carroll ISD. Set behind private gates on 4.83 immaculate acres, this breathtaking estate redefines luxury living in one of Southlake's most coveted enclaves. Designed for both grand-scale entertaining & everyday indulgence, the residence blends timeless sophistication with an extraordinary array of world-class amenities. A sweeping circle drive introduces the stately motor court & 6-car garage, while the resort-inspired grounds invite leisure at every turn-featuring an indoor sports court, sparkling oversized pool & spa, multiple alfresco lounges, a full outdoor kitchen, & dramatic stone fireplace. Every space has been envisioned as the ultimate private retreat for relaxation & entertainment. Inside, artistry & craftsmanship abound. An elevator offers seamless access across levels, while the entertainment wing showcases a game room with wet bar, & a tiered theater, designed for unforgettable moments with family & friends. Wellness & productivity are equally prioritized with a private gym & dual executive offices, each outfitted with custom millwork. The palatial Owner's Retreat is a sanctuary of its own, complete with a spa-inspired bath, dual custom closets (hers with stackable washer-dryer), & a tranquil ambiance that rivals the world's finest resorts. Two main-level guest suites provide comfort & privacy, while upstairs offers 5 additional en-suite bedrooms & 2 living areas for ultimate flexibility. At the heart of the home, the gourmet kitchen is a culinary haven boasting commercial-grade gas cooking, dual dishwashers, built-in refrigeration, double ovens, warming & cooling drawers, & both a butler's pantry & walk-in pantry designed for effortless entertaining. Exuding elegance, exclusivity, & modern convenience, this estate presents a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to own a private Southlake sanctuary of distinction. A residence that must be experienced in person-schedule your private tour today.
